{"tid":1903359,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"義大利行政區長稱中国人吃活老鼠才染疫","createTime":"2020-02-29T02:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T02:53:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4129fdbe58791458f5572e17e8588225a7bb89f2","tid":1903359,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"義大利政壇出現「仇中」現象，北義威內托區長柴亞(Luca Zaia)28日在電視專訪語出驚人地說，義大利人衛生習慣很好不用擔心疫情，中國傷亡慘重是因為「大家都知道，他們愛吃活老鼠」。<br />\n<br />\n威內托大區(Venteto)大區位在北義，該區首府是知名世界水都威尼斯，目前是全義疫情第二嚴重的行政區，確診案例151例。<br />\n<br />\n柴亞28日接受義大利地方電視台「3號天線」(Antenna 3)專訪時表示，義大利疫情爆發一週以來，威內托區確診案例中有63人沒有症狀或狀況良好，只有28人住院，為什麼呢？「原因就是義大利人在衛生習慣和文化方面，都比中國人更有優越性」。<br />\n<br />\n柴亞說，「說實話，大家都看到，中國人愛吃活老鼠」，相對地義大利人的基本衛生素養較高，我們義大利人會洗澡，也常常洗手，義大利人飲食文化也較好，我們知道食物要存放在冰箱，食材有所謂的保存期限。<br />\n<br />\n柴亞表示，中國因為衛生習慣、飲食文化不佳，才會在這場疫情中付出了慘痛的代價。<br />\n<br />\n柴亞說，病毒在骯髒的環境才會擴散，但在義大利沒有這種問題，義大利父母總會不斷提醒孩子，東西掉在地上就不要再吃了。<br />\n<br />\n柴亞的驚人之語，立刻受到義大利主流媒體廣泛引用，包括義大利大報「晚郵報」(Corriere della Sera)、「共和報」(La Repubblica)等都在網站首頁報導。<br />\n<br />\n義大利21日爆發首例本土感染俗稱武漢肺炎的2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)確診案例，7天內案例急遽增加，截至3月1日凌晨已達888例，21人死亡。疫情最嚴重的是以米蘭為首府的倫巴底大區(Lombardia)，確診531例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2053503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2053503&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT292UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=bcc9f1d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2053503</a>"},{"pid":"06e439dd072aa27255d649687b82f660d447ef71","tid":1903359,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pg113HWvZnM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpg113HWvZnM&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT292UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=a1c386f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pg113HWvZnM</a>"},{"pid":"27d0413841c7be7cdee460c3304ef51df8160b46","tid":1903359,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:15:24.000Z","msg":"直接啲話支那人係蝗蟲就得，唔使客氣"},{"pid":"7dd624a0f5fb723ace0378b7986702232a89aae4","tid":1903359,"uid":10338,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"正啦<br />\n意大利旅行<br />\n意甲<br />\n意大利跑車 奢侈品<br />\n意粉 pizza<br />\n支那人全部要抵制未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d71982e46877c8fbed6e9407dec6ec3f5c95f4e","tid":1903359,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"P4病毒研究室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012e0f922ba5e3d6491e89ce2b6aab3ca12992fb","tid":1903359,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcf4a778849475c7a1a445789dcaa067325ac0a","tid":1903359,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d71982e46877c8fbed6e9407dec6ec3f5c95f4e","tid":1903359,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"P4病毒研究室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"P4病毒研究室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531f41b3caf757b360b908bdaaffe66c6872a947","tid":1903359,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"支持排華，支持反共"},{"pid":"cca95bafc6076a20ac355d595fbb7f693ca06f4b","tid":1903359,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"531f41b3caf757b360b908bdaaffe66c6872a947","tid":1903359,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"支持排華，支持反共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02